{"tid":1235554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"月球地下埋藏巨大不明物體","createTime":"2019-06-17T07:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T08:14:38.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1c4e7f0432966ce473e76630ad59b5acc5de3863","tid":1235554,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img2.secretchina.com/pic/2019/6-16/p2447731a471895909-ss.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg2.secretchina.com%2Fpic%2F2019%2F6-16%2Fp2447731a471895909-ss.jpg&h=9ae1b416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖片來源：Adobe Stock）<br />\n<br />\n科學家發現在月球的中央很有可能埋藏了大量的高密度金屬物體，從月球背面地表以下逾半英裡處延伸至地下至少180英裡深處，大小相當於夏威夷島（Big Island，夏威夷群島中最大的一個）的五倍。<br />\n<br />\n這份由美國貝勒大學（Baylor University）的行星地球物理學教授彼得詹姆士（Peter B.James）的研究團隊在研究月球南極艾特肯盆地（South Pole-Aitken Basin）的時候發現了這個未知的大塊物體。他說，「想像一下，把比夏威夷島大五倍的一堆金屬埋在地下，這大概就是我們檢測到的質量」。<br />\n<br />\n研究團隊將測量月球周圍重力得到的數據，與地圖和月球表面的成像對比，他們發現在盆地的底部有大量的金屬物質。再由彼得所提供的彩色月球圖來看，不同的顏色顯示了月球的地形變化，較暖的顏色表示地形較高，較藍的顏色表明地形較低，艾特肯盆地就位在藍色陰影的位置，虛線圓圈則代表該盆地下質量異常的位置。<br />\n<br />\n艾特肯盆地直徑約1600英裡，是太陽系內所有星體上已知的最大盆地之一。它位於月球背向地球的一面，因此從地球上無法直接觀測到。<br />\n<br />\n研究人員還不能確定這個不明物體是什麼。一種猜測認為它可能是撞擊月球形成艾特肯盆地的天體留下的內核，它沒有一路沉進月球的內部，而是滯留在盆地底部以下半英裡深處延伸至約180英裡深處。<br />\n<br />\nNASA的月球專家告訴《國家地理》（National Geographic）雜誌：「這是一個重大發現，為我們了解月球內部構造提供了重要線索。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/06/16/897234.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2019%2F06%2F16%2F897234.html&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0u4Lj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=0e22ffb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2019/06/16/897234.html</a>"},{"pid":"3b3f3bebb6526010d88c054559c7ed26c7bbb3c5","tid":1235554,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:19:06.000Z","msg":"I am"},{"pid":"0b2218b7fda475bf566b023857b5552c14e2a125","tid":1235554,"uid":165683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:19:34.000Z","msg":"secrechina......."},{"pid":"14add4767564659589acbaeb10e298344ca14a2e","tid":1235554,"uid":76216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:19:35.000Z","msg":"天元突破"},{"pid":"e1b1b4da76b749f7f498cb9724c5e750c5a6ffb6","tid":1235554,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:19:37.000Z","msg":"六道地爆天星"},{"pid":"b37b197ebd4177ce2efe475deebc463b2b9c9d5f","tid":1235554,"uid":79789,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:21:29.000Z","msg":"應該係納粹黨黎🤣"},{"pid":"9320e3c3a8e2d2b0a35d537864a0b4ae6772565e","tid":1235554,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:21:46.000Z","msg":"快去掘<br />\n快"},{"pid":"c9b33dc7d15fecb76e5ccf58c1e6a8d76283addd","tid":1235554,"uid":237425,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:23:42.000Z","msg":"唔知睇過咩傳言<br />\n話月球係人造<br />\n入面係金屬骨架基地<br />\n外面扮天然星體樣<br />\n<br />\n十足十死星咁"},{"pid":"ae57a9a9a887c0720638815b443f155ee3437ca0","tid":1235554,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:24:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7b41212881602d41ae246eaf7ab7ae9f535c6d","tid":1235554,"uid":120057,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:26:01.000Z","msg":"超銀河紅蓮螺巖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5433721043bea31b30fc1c6bb162fa5b19988274","tid":1235554,"uid":207792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf0b2157347fc38cf628a34693d061eb8eb41fb","tid":1235554,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:27:32.000Z","msg":"Tran